===[[Season 2]]===
Before leaving the [[Red Keep]] to oversee [[King's Landing]]'s defenses against [[Stannis Baratheon]]'s attack, King Joffrey orders [[Sansa Stark]] to see him off with a kiss. He then draws Hearteater and commands her to kiss it. He mentions that after the battle he will have her kiss it again and taste his uncle's blood. Sansa asked if that means he will be fighting the vanguard, as [[Robb Stark]], who is only a pretender, does. Angered, Joffrey says that someday she can lick Robb's blood off Hearteater as well. Ultimately,Â Joffrey never wields the sword in battle.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Blackwater]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

===[[Season 3]]===
Joffrey has Hearteater with him inside his palanquin as he is being transported through [[Flea Bottom]].&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Valar Dohaeris]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
